    public final class PrometheusMetricCollectingClient<T extends MetricLabel<T>,I extends Request,O extends Response>
extends SimpleDecoratingClient<I,O>
    Decorates a Client to collect metrics into Prometheus CollectorRegistry. To use, simply prepare a CollectorRegistry and add this decorator to a service specification.
